1
00:01:11,520 --> 00:01:12,320
Come in.

2
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:19,480
Sit down.

3
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:31,320
I trust I've given everyone a satisfactory answer this time.

4
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:36,640
On behalf of the villagers of Dayang Village,

5
00:01:37,440 --> 00:01:38,240
thank you.

6
00:01:39,360 --> 00:01:41,400
I should have done this a long time ago.

7
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:42,759
There is one more thing.

8
00:01:42,759 --> 00:01:44,600
Our company has established a foundation.

9
00:01:44,600 --> 00:01:47,000
We need a credible representative to distribute the supplies.

10
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,640
You were elected by the staff.

11
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:50,240
I'm entrusting this responsibility to you.

12
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:52,440
The children are waiting for this help.

13
00:01:54,720 --> 00:01:57,780
But the real obstacle to Dayang Village's development

14
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:00,930
is Xiao Tianman.

15
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:02,240
I know.

16
00:02:02,720 --> 00:02:04,560
He certainly won't let this go.

17
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:07,020
So we need to take the initiative.

18
00:02:09,039 --> 00:02:10,240
Take the initiative?

19
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:12,920
How?

20
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:15,320
I've asked Du Jing to look for

21
00:02:15,320 --> 00:02:17,200
news about Jiang Xiaomei's parents.

22
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:19,040
If the whole family had returned to the provincial capital,

23
00:02:19,040 --> 00:02:20,600
we would have heard something.

24
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:23,079
So this must be related to Xiao Tianman.

25
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:25,240
I think this is our breakthrough.

26
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:30,800
So Jiang Xiaomei is Xiao Tianman's weakness,

27
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:31,520
right?

28
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,160
Right.

29
00:02:43,920 --> 00:02:45,880
Run. Keep running.

30
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:49,450
Do you think Xiao Tianman can protect you?

31
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:50,640
Stay back.

32
00:02:50,640 --> 00:02:52,400
He's the one who told me you were here.

33
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:54,120
I... I said stay back.

34
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:56,280
I... I'm begging you.

35
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:58,520
Please.

36
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:00,400
I'm begging you. Begging you.

37
00:03:01,040 --> 00:03:02,880
Chief Sun, I was wrong.

38
00:03:02,920 --> 00:03:04,960
Please. I was wrong.

39
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,200
Help!

40
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:10,240
I was wrong. Please.

41
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,480
I was wrong.

42
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:23,560
Boss.

43
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:26,360
I don't want those.

44
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:28,079
Xiaomei.

45
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:31,160
No one dares to buy what you've touched.

46
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,650
I can only sell it to you.

47
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:34,280
Yeah, Xiaomei.

48
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:36,960
One minute it's Factory Manager Xiao, the next it's Factory Manager Li.

49
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:39,290
People think anything you touch is dirty.

50
00:03:43,040 --> 00:03:43,840
20.

51
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:27,000
What is this?

52
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:43,520
Aren't these intimate photos of you and Section Chief Sun?

53
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:48,680
Actually,

54
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:50,680
you two are quite a match.

55
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:54,040
You used me.

56
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,320
What use are you?

57
00:05:02,320 --> 00:05:04,780
President Xiao was just giving you a chance.

58
00:05:05,280 --> 00:05:06,720
Someone like you

59
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:09,440
is a dime a dozen.

60
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:16,020
You didn't really think President Xiao fell in love with you, did you?

61
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,280
You're so naive.

62
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:19,080
So stupid.

63
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,200
Let me tell you,

64
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:26,040
you'll get every penny you're owed.

65
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:28,450
Take it and get the hell out.

66
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:33,200
Bastard.

67
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,159
You're all bastards.

68
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:48,680
Gang.

69
00:05:50,400 --> 00:05:51,200
Gang.

70
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:57,060
Something happened to Xiaofang.

71
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,280
Xiaofang.

72
00:06:01,840 --> 00:06:03,920
Who did this?

73
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,000
I'm fine.

74
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:07,040
I went home after grocery shopping this morning,

75
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:09,400
and saw a lot of people rummaging through my house.

76
00:06:09,400 --> 00:06:10,440
I was scared,

77
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:12,720
so I fell a few times while running away.

78
00:06:13,080 --> 00:06:14,720
Shouldn't we call the police?

79
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:15,920
Don't call the police.

80
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:16,720
What's wrong?

81
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:18,720
Xiaofang.

82
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:22,130
Are you keeping something from us?

83
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:27,200
It's okay.

84
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:29,440
Just say it.

85
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:37,490
There is indeed something.

86
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:40,320
Be careful.

87
00:06:45,960 --> 00:06:47,960
Found it. That's right.

88
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:49,900
It's right under here.

89
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:51,240
Are you sure?

90
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:51,960
I'm sure.

91
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:52,800
I marked the spot.

92
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:53,520
Okay.

93
00:06:53,520 --> 00:06:54,960
Dig. It's here.

94
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:09,040
It's out.

95
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:16,040
It's a ledger.

96
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:28,080
It's full of Xiao Tianman's illegal accounts.

97
00:07:28,080 --> 00:07:29,210
Records of bribery.

98
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:32,720
The names and amounts are all there.

99
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:37,250
Xiaomei also said she hid a voice recorder in the office.

100
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:38,720
She wouldn't listen to reason back then.

101
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:41,450
She insisted on going back to the office to get it.

102
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:43,320
It wasn't that simple.

103
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:46,320
You know what kind of person Xiao Tianman is.

104
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:47,720
He would never let her go.

105
00:08:46,680 --> 00:08:47,480
Who is it?

106
00:08:50,800 --> 00:08:51,480
Xiaomei.

107
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:54,080
Sis.

108
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:58,660
Here is all the evidence of Xiao Tianman's bribery.

109
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,860
You must keep this safe for me.

110
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:08,840
What is this?

111
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:19,800
Xiao Tianman is a monster.

112
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:23,320
He didn't just make me his mistress.

113
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:25,880
He even gave me away to someone else.

114
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:28,320
I'll book a ticket for you right now.

115
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:29,640
Go hide in the city.

116
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,720
As long as we have the ledger,

117
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:38,840
he can't do anything to us.

118
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:42,540
I'll make him pay back everything he owes me.

119
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,880
Don't go.

120
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:47,920
That's Xiao Tianman.

121
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:50,280
You can't fight him.

122
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:57,680
You must protect this ledger for me.

123
00:09:57,680 --> 00:10:00,800
This is the key evidence

124
00:10:00,800 --> 00:10:03,130
that will let the law punish Xiao Tianman.

125
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:05,000
So,

126
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:08,640
Jiang Xiaomei stole Xiao Tianman's ledger

127
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,640
to blackmail him.

128
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:13,180
She wanted to buy her freedom, right?

129
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,620
Why didn't you tell us sooner?

130
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:17,560
Do you know how dangerous this is?

131
00:10:17,560 --> 00:10:20,320
I was scared. Scared of dragging you into it.

132
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:22,840
I didn't expect to be found today.

133
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:25,090
This doesn't look good.

134
00:10:25,760 --> 00:10:28,290
Xiao Tianman knows you still have his ledger.

135
00:10:28,880 --> 00:10:30,480
He'll definitely come back.

136
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:31,770
I don't think so.

137
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:34,580
Xiaomei wouldn't sell me out. She wouldn't.

138
00:10:34,680 --> 00:10:36,080
If Xiao Tianman knew,

139
00:10:38,520 --> 00:10:40,180
Xiaofang would be dead by now.

140
00:10:40,760 --> 00:10:41,560
Right.

141
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:42,760
Right.

142
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:45,360
There's so much in this ledger.

143
00:10:46,520 --> 00:10:48,840
Enough to put him away for several lifetimes.

144
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:50,370
Let's hand it to the police.

145
00:10:50,560 --> 00:10:53,960
Can you be sure that if we hand it over,

146
00:10:54,880 --> 00:10:57,160
there aren't Xiao Tianman's people in the force?

147
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:59,040
Can you be sure this ledger

148
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:01,840
will actually be investigated?

149
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:04,840
What do we do?

150
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:08,440
Xiaofang,

151
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:12,880
did you see clearly before you were knocked out?

152
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:14,420
Was it Xiao Tianman's men?

153
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:17,920
No.

154
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:19,860
They had their faces covered.

155
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,720
Could it be Liao Fei?

156
00:11:24,480 --> 00:11:25,610
I'll go ask Liao Fei.

157
00:11:26,520 --> 00:11:28,980
Our three-day deadline is almost up anyway.

158
00:11:29,680 --> 00:11:31,080
I'll settle everything.

159
00:11:31,280 --> 00:11:33,440
Brother, I'll go with you to meet him.

160
00:11:34,560 --> 00:11:35,360
No need.

161
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:37,920
You and Yongzi take care of Xiaofang.

162
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:38,880
Keep her safe.

163
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,120
I'll go alone.

164
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,720
No. This is my responsibility.

165
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:43,080
I have to go, Brother.

166
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,660
No one is to blame for this.

167
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:49,160
It was an accident. Kid, trust me.

168
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:55,320
Xiaofang, it's okay now.

169
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:56,960
Don't worry.
